headline: Has Northern Trust’s 2025 Rally Already Priced In Its Growth Potential?
summary: Wondering if Northern Trust is still worth buying after its big run up, or if the easy money has already been made? This breakdown will help you decide whether the current price really stacks up against its fundamentals. The stock has quietly kept climbing, with the share price now around $132 after rising 0.6% over the last week, 3.5% over the past month, and 28.3% year to date, building on 24.9% over 1 year and more than 65% over 3 and 5 years.
